Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事 kwsk
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近编写这个安全系统的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让其告诉自己密码
