Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香是「魔法少女阁下大人」的女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神错乱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被洗脑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…总之 就是这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 Frau
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的任务完成后 就会飞去菲律宾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说在那里可以重新见到老婆和小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知如此 就不该相信他人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里蹲就要有家里蹲的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直独自一人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dhufufu
