Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有我可以帮上忙的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之咱相信是没问题的！还有我会送去力量的！力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买了慰问品准备去你那边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按门铃后请开门让我进去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于暗号请向取消的方向努力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为我为什么会变成家里蹲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道 因为你不擅长和他人交流？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确答案是为了制作KILLBALA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「GUNVARREL」也以那样的方式告终
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:52.14,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300, 300)}▌弃番
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:52.35,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:52.14,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300, 300)}弃番（オワコン）\N结束的番组（終わったコンテンツ）的简写，否定在一定时间内掀起热潮的\N近期动画或游戏的网络用语，多用来嘲笑在一定时间内十分流行但现在声势\N已大不如前的作品。出典来自2ch上围绕《凉宫春日的忧郁》所产生的骚动。\N虽然此作曾引发热潮，但因为原作轻小说长期延期，赞否两极的永无止境的八月，\N还有团长CV平野绫的骚动导致在2010年左右“凉宫春日这东西是结束的番组啦”\N这句话得到了爆发性流行。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我害怕它会变成弃番
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果大家忘记「GUNVARREL」的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也会变成被人遗忘的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我决定用「GUNVARREL」为题材制作游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连去学校的时间也舍不得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了「GUNVARREL」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长喜欢KILLBALA吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 我觉得是一款制作精良的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.10,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,660)}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此表扬这个游戏 我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说了很喜欢 我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是不是性欲旺盛了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…好像连旺盛的精力都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微保持这样一会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「GUNVARREL」对我来说是重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无比重要的作品噢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妈妈留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承载了许多关于妈妈的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 学长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「GUNVARREL」还能再次绽放出光芒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 先着手于制GUNVARREL2
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它参加世博会不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到这座岛 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为遇见了八汐学长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 八汐学长 要赢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是为了我和妈妈也行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古郡小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想了解一下东京事件的相关情况
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古郡小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:15:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小秋他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古郡小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能开一下门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是警官吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个 请救救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 那到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快 这是最后的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁警察回来之前 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 这次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的生命槽变红的时候 就会使用外挂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准那个时机 要是能成功发动慢镜头的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我一给信号 你就把等级调到最大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持住 还差一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点 还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在 可奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见了
