Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长 太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经输入停止机能的指令了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好…了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八汐学长 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.78,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,660)}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:49.08,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京大停电已经过去一周了
